Package: namesilo-ddns
Version: 1.2.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: OpenAI <support@example.invalid>
Depends: bash, curl, dnsutils, libxml2-utils, systemd
Description: NameSilo DDNS updater with systemd timer integration
 A production-oriented NameSilo DDNS updater for Debian 13.
 .
 The package installs:
  - a oneshot updater script,
  - a systemd service,
  - a systemd timer using OnBootSec=30s and OnUnitInactiveSec=5min,
  - a default configuration file under /etc/default,
  - and documentation under /usr/share/doc/namesilo-ddns.
